<!-- Game Cheats Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Fight as the R1 robot -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Enter the character selection screen. Highlight Danbain and press [Triangle]. Highlight Elgaim and press [Triangle]. Highlight Z Gundam and press [Triangle]. Highlight Danbain and press [Triangle]. Highlight DI Custom and press [Triangle]. The R1 robot will appear next to GX Divide</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Fight as the R2 robot -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Enter the character selection screen. Highlight Z Gundam and press [Triangle]x2. Highlight DI Custom and press [Triangle]. Highlight Danbain and press [Triangle]. Highlight DI Custom and press [Triangle]. The R2 robot will appear to the right of the R1 robot</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Fight as Boss -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Highlight the R1 robot and press [Triangle]. Highlight the R2 robot and press [Triangle]. Highlight the R3 robot and press [Triangle]. Highlight the R1 robot and press [Triangle]. Highlight Garia and press [Triangle]. Boss will appear between the R3 robot and Garia</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; CG Gallery mode -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Hold Down/Left + Triangle + X and press Start on pad two at the title screen</font>&nbsp;<br>
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ACTION REPLAY CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Infinite health Player 1 -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>800A756C 0080</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Infinite health Player 2 -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>800A7618 0080</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Infinite Time -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>800606A8 0984</font>&nbsp;<br>
	 </tr>
	</table>
